<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">
		
<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Midori Makibao is a small white racehorse. Compared to other thoroughbred horses, he looks more like a donkey with wide nostrils. However, with his guts and speed as his weapon, Makibao wins in every big race.
                  <br><br>In the beginning of his career, Makibao had a trouble making his debut as a racehorse, because of his appearance and various disadvantages he had. But Makibao had reasons to overcome his difficulties; there was a lifelong rival horse called Superhorse Cascade, that Makibao needed to defeat. Plus, he was determined to win back his mother, a horse that had been taken away for pay back the debt on the farm.
                  <br><br>There are many hardships that Makibao has to overcome, but he thrives in the series of races to become a great racehorse.
                  <br><br>The Playstation game is a mix between an adventure mode and a racing mode. The adventure part is a choice of different actions and the racing part is in third person perspective and the gameplay is just pressing the proper buttons in the proper way to run faster.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Voices of the street and anime voice actor animated cut scenes that extend to several thousand that have been painted for this game cause liven up the drama. In addition, all of the special training and the race has become a key combo action game based on a combination of buttons.
                  <br>Special training and race heated by a key combo you can play this action.
                  <br>With rival horse horse "mating", is a nail of the race "fully follow", five types of special training is "swimming" in a thrilling guts "chipping down forest", and "ramp" of yell.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>First & third person perspectives.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Anime & horse racing themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

